      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-up delay-200 price-card bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-[0px_8px_24px_rgba(23,29,25,0.04)] hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">search_check</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-3 tracking-tight">Phí kiểm định chất lượng</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Chi phí kiểm tra chất lượng sản phẩm bằng <strong>0.05% giá trị lô hàng</strong>, dao động từ 700,000 — 10,000,000 VNĐ (chưa bao gồm VAT).</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-up price-card bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-[0px_8px_24px_rgba(23,29,25,0.04)] hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">construction</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-3 tracking-tight">Phí nâng hạ hàng</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Hàng thông thường: <strong>miễn phí</strong>. Hàng quá khổ, quá tải cần cẩu: phí thuê cẩu tính riêng theo thực tế phát sinh.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-up delay-100 price-card bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-[0px_8px_24px_rgba(23,29,25,0.04)] hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">delivery_dining</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-3 tracking-tight">Phí giao hàng nội địa</h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">Nhận tại kho Hà Nội: <strong>miễn phí</strong>. Giao tận nơi trong Hà Nội và các tỉnh lân cận: phát sinh thêm cước ship nội địa.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal reveal-up delay-200 price-card bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 rounded-[2rem] shadow-[0px_8px_24px_rgba(23,29,25,0.04)] hover:shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-secondary-container rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">warehouse</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold text-on-surface mb-3 tracking-tight">Phí lưu kho</h3>
